					    <!-- IMAGE CREDIT -->
				        													
				<div class="post_content_body_wrapper">
    			<div class="post_header_wrapper">
    									<h1 class="post_title" itemprop="headline">
					New on the Lit Hub Podcast: The Windham-Campbell Prizes and A New Literary Tabloid					</h1>
					<h3>Featuring Michael Kelleher, Sammy Loren, and Drew Broussard</h3>
				</div>
								<div class="author_info" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
					<div class="author_name">By&nbsp;<a href="https://lithub.com/author/thelithubpodcast/" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">The Lit Hub Podcast&nbsp;</span></a></div>
					<div class="author_hr"><hr/></div>
					<div class="publish_date">March 28, 2025</div>
				</div>
				<div class="social_links">
										<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?via=lithub&text=New+on+the+Lit+Hub+Podcast%3A+The+Windham-Campbell+Prizes+and+A+New+Literary+Tabloid&url=https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fnew-on-the-lit-hub-podcast-the-windham-campbell-prizes-and-a-new-literary-tabloid%2F"><span class="social_twitter"></span></a>
					<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fnew-on-the-lit-hub-podcast-the-windham-campbell-prizes-and-a-new-literary-tabloid%2F&t=New+on+the+Lit+Hub+Podcast%3A+The+Windham-Campbell+Prizes+and+A+New+Literary+Tabloid"><span class="social_facebook"></span></a>
									</div>
									<!-- Begin each blog post -->
					<div class="post_wrapper" style="padding-top:0;">
						<div class="post_inner_wrapper">
					    	<div class="post_wrapper_inner">
								<div class="post_inner_wrapper">
							        
									<span itemprop="articleBody"><p><em>A weekly behind-the-scenes dive into everything interesting, dynamic, strange, and wonderful happening in literary culture—featuring Lit Hub staff, columnists, and special guests! Hosted by Drew Broussard.</em></p>
<p>You might be mistaken in thinking that it&#8217;s a real high-culture/low-culture episode this week, but really it&#8217;s an all-joy-culture episode. Drew kicks things off with a quick nod to National Short Story Month before talking to Michael Kelleher about the 2025 Windham-Campbell Prizes and what makes the prize so special. Then, he chats with Sammy Loren about the new literary tabloid <em>On the Rag</em> and why pitching a broader, messier tent is a good idea. Go chase something that makes you (and, ideally, other people too) happy, damn it!</p>
<p><iframe src="https://playlist.megaphone.fm?e=LIT3417587622" width="100%" height="200" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>The Lit Hub Podcast is a production of Lit Hub Radio and is <a href="https://link.chtbl.com/TheLitHubPodcast" class="external" target="_blank">available wherever you get your podcasts</a>; music by Dani Lencioni of Evelyn; Engineering and production by Stardust House</em><em><a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/the-lit-hub-podcast/id1766519889" class="external" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" data-attachment-id="243207" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/campus-repression-and-remixing-proust-lol-this-week-on-the-lit-hub-podcast/apple-2/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/apple.png" data-orig-size="438,440" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="apple" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/apple-300x300.png" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/apple.png" class="wp-image-243207 aligncenter" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/apple.png" alt="" width="74" height="74" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/apple.png 438w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/apple-300x300.png 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/apple-150x150.png 150w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/apple-60x60.png 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/apple-109x109.png 109w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/apple-100x100.png 100w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/apple-50